ious/other fruit</b>: <a href="/wiki/Cr%C3%A8me_de_banane" title="Crème de banane" class="mw-redirect">Crème de banane</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Cr%C3%A8me_de_cassis" title="Crème de cassis">Crème de cassis</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Limoncello" title="Limoncello">Limoncello</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Schnapps#American_Schnapps" title="Schnapps">Schnapps</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Sloe_gin" title="Sloe gin">Sloe gin</a></span></div>
